name: Moustache Greetings
description:
Learn to say hello in many moustaches!

Note cards are A2 size measuring 4" x 5.5" and are paired with a coordinating envelope.

(1) each of:

-Hey
-Odelay
-Konnichiwa
-Bonjour
-Charmed
-Howdy

Cards are digitally offset printed on 110 lb. white card stock and open from the top. Blank inside for your personal notes.

You choose envelope color! Choose from red, orange, yellow, blue, white, or kraft. Specify envelope color in buyer's notes. If no color is specified, one will be chosen for you.

Sold as a set of 6 and packaged in a cello sleeve with a signature label. Makes a great gift when paired with other items from my shop!

name: Buck Gift Tags
description:
A set of 8 gift tags featuring a young buck in love.  Perfect for a gift or a quick note.

Tags are flat printed on 80 lb. recycled card stock and cut by hand.  Due to the nature of the handmade process, slight variations in product are natural.

name: Cottontail Minis
